text: Gladys Berejiklian (born 22 September 1970) is an Armenian Australian politician. She was the 45th Premier of New South Wales from 23 January 2019 until 5 October 2021."Gladys Berejiklian: skyâ€™s the limit for self-made Liberal", The Australian, 20 January 2017. Retrieved 20 January 2017. She is the Leader of the New South Wales Liberal Party. She has been a member of the New South Wales Legislative Assembly from 2003 to 2021, representing the seat of Willoughby. Berejiklian was born in Sydney. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Premiers of New South Wales Category:Politicians from Sydney
